reviewText: Agree bleach is awesome. I just wish they had a 4 pack of all the movies on blu ray.

I've always been a big fan of Bleach the series and when I saw this movie set I had to buy this and the other set as well. This is extremely awesome as you get both movies for the price of one. I highly recommend this to anyone looking to buy the movies.
I LOVE these movies. The double feature is super cost effective too. It's way cheaper to buy them like this than to buy them individually.
